column6: SELECT d.name , SUM(frame_len) as 'bytes', case when d.name like 'server%' then 100000 else 100 end as 'min', case when d.name like 'server%' then 100000000 else 100000 end as 'max'

column16: FROM mtd.packet_logs l, mtd.devices d where d.ipv4 = l.ip_src and ip_src <> ' ' and ip_dst <> ' '

column6: group by d.name order by SUM(frame_len) desc;
